OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FMeta boss Mark Zuckerberg will face
OL,7,Fgrieving families when he testifies on
OL,8,FWednesday at a landmark social media
OL,9,Faddiction trial in Los Angeles.
OL,11,FThe world's biggest social media
OL,12,Fcompanies will feature in several
OL,13,Ftrials this year, which seek to hold
OL,14,Fthem responsible for harms to children
OL,15,Fwho use their platforms.
OL,17,FInstagram's parent company Meta, and
OL,18,FGoogle's YouTube both face claims that
OL,19,Ftheir platforms are deliberately
OL,20,Faddictive and harm children.
