OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FBoth TikTok and Snapchat's parent
OL,7,Fcompany, Snap Inc., were originally
OL,8,Fnamed in the lawsuit, but settled for
OL,9,Fundisclosed sums.
OL,11,FZuckerberg is expected to attend the
OL,12,Ftrial in person.
OL,14,FProceedings are being compared to the
OL,15,FBig Tobacco trials that led to a 1998
OL,16,Fsettlement requiring cigarette
OL,17,Fcompanies to pay billions in health
OL,18,Fcare costs and restrict marketing
OL,19,Ftargeting minors.
