OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FThe trial kicked off last week, with
OL,7,FInstagram boss Adam Mosseri testifying
OL,8,Fthat he disagrees with the idea that
OL,9,Fpeople can be clinically addicted to
OL,10,Fsocial media platforms.
OL,12,FMosseri, who has headed Instagram
OL,13,Fsince 2018, said it's important to
OL,14,Fdifferentiate between clinical
OL,15,Faddiction and what he called
OL,16,Fproblematic use.
OL,18,FWhat is the case about?
