OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FAt the core of the Los Angeles case is
OL,7,Fa 20-year-old identified only by the
OL,8,Finitials "KGM," whose case could
OL,9,Fdetermine how thousands of similar
OL,10,Flawsuits will play out. Addiction
OL,11,Fforms a key pillar of the case.
OL,13,FShe was a minor when she said she
OL,14,Fbecame addicted to social media, which
OL,15,Fshe claims exacerbated depression and
OL,16,Fsuicidal thoughts.
