OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FKGM and the cases of two other
OL,7,Fplaintiffs have been selected to be
OL,8,Fbellwether trials - essentially test
OL,9,Fcases for both sides to see how their
OL,10,Farguments play out before a jury.
OL,12,FLawyer for the plaintiff Mark Lanier
OL,13,Fsaid the companies' lawyers will "try
OL,14,Fto blame the little girl and her
OL,15,Fparents for the trap they built."
OL,17,FWednesday will mark the first time
OL,18,FZuckerberg testifies about youth
OL,19,Fsafety claims before a jury.
