OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FIf the jury sides against Zuckerberg
OL,7,Fand other defendants, it could set a
OL,8,Fprecedent for holding social media
OL,9,Fcompanies responsible for harmful or
OL,10,Fdangerous design decisions.
OL,12,FIt comes off the back of years of tech
OL,13,Fgiants fending off lawsuits with the
OL,14,Fcontent liability shield, known as
OL,15,FSection 230, which protects tech
OL,16,Fcompanies from liability for material
OL,17,Fposted on their platforms.
OL,19,FWhat makes this court case different?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
