OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FIt is the first time that social media
OL,7,Fcompanies face a trial by jury.
OL,9,FJurors are tasked with deciding
OL,10,Fwhether social media companies were
OL,11,Fnegligent when creating and amending
OL,12,Ftheir products to encourage people to
OL,13,Fspend more time on them, rather than
OL,14,Fwhether specific content on the
OL,15,Fplatforms was harmful.
OL,17,FSomething that has come up already in
OL,18,Fthe case is "infinite scrolling" -
OL,19,Fwhen your feed doesn't end, no matter
OL,20,Fhow long you spend on it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
