OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FLuis Li, the attorney representing
OL,7,FYouTube and Google, delivered an
OL,8,Fopening statement last week focused on
OL,9,FKGM's user data, claiming the five-
OL,10,Fyear average of her watch time is 29
OL,11,Fminutes per day.
OL,13,FHe said KGM's average daily time spent
OL,14,Fon YouTube Shorts, watching vertical
OL,15,Fshort-form videos with the "infinite
OL,16,Fscroll" feature, was just 1 minute and
OL,17,F14 seconds.
