OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FHe also told jurors that all of the
OL,7,FYouTube features Lanier challenged in
OL,8,Fhis opening statement could be
OL,9,Fdisabled and modified to match users'
OL,10,Fpreferences.
OL,12,F"When you strip away all of the
OL,13,Frhetoric ... what you are left with is
OL,14,Fa simple truth. Infinite scroll is not
OL,15,Finfinite," Li said.
