OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,F"In some cases, in this case, before
OL,7,Fthis court, before you, the jury, it's
OL,8,Fas little as a minute and 14 seconds.
OL,9,FIt's not social media addiction when
OL,10,Fit's not social media and it's not an
OL,11,Faddiction."
OL,13,FWhat happens if tech companies lose?
OL,15,FIf the companies involved lose the
OL,16,Fcase, they may be forced to change the
OL,17,Fdesign of their platforms going
OL,18,Fforward.
