OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FAnd, while TikTok and Snapchat have
OL,7,Falready settled in this case, that
OL,8,Fwon't stop them from being involved in
OL,9,Fsubsequent cases.
OL,11,FComparing social media platforms to
OL,12,Fcasinos and addictive drugs, lawyer
OL,13,FMark Lanier said the case will be as
OL,14,F"easy as ABC" - which stands for
OL,15,F"addicting the brains of children."
OL,17,FHe said Meta and Google, "two of the
OL,18,Frichest corporations in history," have
OL,19,F"engineered addiction in children's
OL,20,Fbrains."
