OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FHe presented jurors with a slew of
OL,7,Finternal emails, documents, and
OL,8,Fstudies conducted by Meta and YouTube,
OL,9,Fas well as YouTube's parent company,
OL,10,FGoogle.
OL,12,FHe emphasised the findings of a study
OL,13,FMeta conducted called "Project Myst,"
OL,14,Fin which they surveyed 1,000 teens and
OL,15,Ftheir parents about their social media
OL,16,Fuse.
