OL,3,CChildren, addiction and social media:
OL,4,CWhy is Mark Zuckerberg in court?
OL,6,FThe two major findings, Lanier said,
OL,7,Fwere that Meta knew children who
OL,8,Fexperienced "adverse events" like
OL,9,Ftrauma and stress were particularly
OL,10,Fvulnerable to addiction; and that
OL,11,Fparental supervision and controls made
OL,12,Flittle impact.
OL,14,FHe also highlighted internal Google
OL,15,Fdocuments that likened some company
OL,16,Fproducts to a casino, and internal
OL,17,Fcommunication between Meta employees
OL,18,Fin which one person said Instagram is
OL,19,F"like a drug" and they are "basically
OL,20,Fpushers."
